org.apache.gearpump.streaming.metrics

Class ProcessorAggregator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.gearpump.streaming.metrics.ProcessorAggregator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetricsAggregator

    public class ProcessorAggregator
extends java.lang.Object
implements MetricsAggregator
    Does aggregation on metrics after grouping by these three attributes: 1. processorId 2. time section(represented as a index integer) 3. metricName(like sendThroughput)

    It assumes that for each MasterToClient.HistoryMetricsItem, the name follow the format app(appId).processor(processorId).task(taskId).(metricName)

    It parses the name to get processorId and metricName. If the parsing fails, then current MasterToClient.HistoryMetricsItem will be skipped.

    NOTE: this class is optimized for performance.
